          "type": "question",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "title": "<strong>What's included in Heybike 4th Anniversary Celebration?</strong>",
            "text": "<p>We're celebrating 4 amazing years with unbeatable deals and exciting gifts! Here's what you can enjoy:</p><ul><li><strong>Best Deals Ever</strong> on All Ebikes</li><li><strong>Extra $100 Coupon</strong> with code \"ANNIVERSARY\"</li><li><strong>Free Baskets</strong> with select models</li><li><strong>60-Day Price Match Guarantee</strong></li><li><strong>One Tree Planted</strong> for every ebike sold</li></ul><p>Even more anniversary giveaways & surprises await! Stay in the loop—<a href=\"https://www.heybike.com/account/register\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.heybike.com/account/register\"><em><strong>subscribe</strong></em></a> to our emails for exclusive offers and the latest event updates!</p>",
